# =====================================================
# SECURITY NOTES
# =====================================================

# 🔒 Never commit this file with real values!
# 🔒 Keep tokens secret (use .gitignore)
# 🔒 Use environment variables in production
# 🔒 Rotate tokens regularly
# 🔒 Delete old tokens you don't use

# Check your .gitignore includes:
# .env
# .env.local
# .env.*.local

# =====================================================
# TROUBLESHOOTING
# =====================================================

# If "Supabase connection failed":
# 1. Is SUPABASE_URL correct? Should end with .supabase.co
# 2. Is SUPABASE_KEY the "anon public" key (not service role)?
# 3. Can you access Supabase dashboard? Network issue?
# 4. Did you enable API access in Supabase settings?

# If "HuggingFace token invalid":
# 1. Is HF_TOKEN a valid token? (starts with "hf_")
# 2. Did you select "Read" access when creating it?
# 3. Is token not expired? (tokens don't expire, but can be revoked)
# 4. Did you accept agreements in HF? (for pyannote)

# If "API_BASE not responding":
# 1. Is HF Space deployed? Check status on HF
# 2. Did you include full URL? (with https:// and .hf.space)
# 3. Is API running? Check Space logs
# 4. Did you set environment variables in Space?

# =====================================================
# USE IN DIFFERENT ENVIRONMENTS
# =====================================================

